song.title: <m> the abyss
song.info:
Composed by matrix on the 3th of may in the year 1992.
this zak was inspired by the great movie and a picture drawn by wyatt, the gfx-man of our group : gentlemen!
info update! later we changed the name of the group to "dolby c" and this zak actually became music-compo winner at a party in hungary.
